# 02 — .gitignore

Copy/paste this into a file named **.gitignore** at the repo root.

```gitignore
# --- OS / Editor ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- Node / JS ---
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# --- Rust / Cargo ---
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock

# --- Tauri ---
# local build artifacts
src-tauri/target/
# generated by tauri dev/build
src-tauri/gen/

# --- Env / Secrets ---
.env
.env.*

# --- Build outputs (your release folder) ---
release_out/
dist/

# --- Misc ---
*.log

# If you store screenshots locally
screenshots/
```
